tablet racks~
The tablet racks hold layered copies in Littoral Branch notation, each copy paired with a modern gloss so patrol readers can follow old legal syntax. Salt has blurred several witness strokes, but restoration notes pinned beside the racks explain which symbols still carry authority and which were retired after the Fracture Era.
