Sun-Glared Spur of the Reach carries the Reach's long memory, with each era leaving traces instead of clean replacements.  Kite shadows cross the flats in long arcs that travelers mistake for moving landmarks.  The fast line rewards confidence only when paired with discipline and route memory.  Dawn and dusk draw most crossings, when reflection weakens enough for marker lines to reappear.  From here, movement commits north with little opportunity to hedge the decision.
